Package: triviz
Type: Package
Title: Triangular Visualizations for the Significance of Pairwise 
    Differences in Multigroup Comparisons
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Denis", "Cohen", email = "denis.cohen@mzes.uni-mannheim.de", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Andreas", "KÃ¼pfer", email = "akuepfer@mail.uni-mannheim.de", role = "aut"))
Description: The \code{triviz} package offers functions for
    plotting group-specific estimates along with information on the
    uncertainty about all of their pairwise differences. Next to
    static \code{ggplot2}-based plotting functions, it also offers
    tools for the in-depth exploration of these pairwise differences
    via interactive \code{shiny} Apps.
